      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i'm prepping for my school debate tournament and im stuck. can u tell me which side of the illegal immigration debate is actually more morally defensible: the argument for stricter border security or the argument for humanitarian asylum? i need to know which one has the stronger moral ground so i can prep my opening.",
